devdoc.details: This Contract forms File Storage / Stamping / Encryption part of Hydro Protocols

acceptFileTransfer(uint256,uint256,uint2.details: Function to accept file transfer from a user

params._fileIndex: is the index where file is stored
params._groupIndex: is the index of the group where the file is suppose to be for the recipient
params._transferSpecificIndex: is the file mapping stored no the recipient transfers mapping
params._transfereeEIN: is the EIN of the user to whom the file needs to be transferred

params._encrypted: defines if the file is encrypted or not
params._encryptedHash: defines the encrypted public key password for the sender address
params._groupIndex: defines the index of the group of file
params._hash: is the hash of the stored file
params._metadata: is the data stored for protocol usage
params._name: is the name of the file

addToBlacklist(uint256).details: Remove a non-owner user to blacklist

params._nonOwnerEIN: is the ein of the recipient

addToWhitelist(uint256).details: Add a non-owner user to whitelist

params._nonOwnerEIN: is the ein of the recipient

cancelFileTransfer(uint256,uint256,uint2.details: Function to cancel file transfer inititated by the current owner

params._fileIndex: is the index where file is stored
params._transfereeEIN: is the EIN of the user to whom the file needs to be transferred

params._fileIndex: is the index where file is stored
params._name: is the name of stored file

createGroup(uint256,string).details: Create a new Group for the user
